---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions | ScamCheck" description="Terms and Conditions for TrafficTicketScamCheck.com. Read the terms of use for our free traffic ticket scam verification tool.">
  <Nav />
  <main class="w-full flex flex-col">
    <section class="w-full py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <h1 class="text-display-md md:text-display-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-4">Terms & Conditions</h1>
        <p class="text-body text-mute mb-8">Last updated: June 29, 2026</p>

        <div class="prose space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-heading-md font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-body text-body leading-relaxed">
              By accessing and using TrafficTicketScamCheck.com ("ScamCheck"), you agree to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please do not use this website.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-heading-md font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Description of Service</h2>
            <p class="text-body text-body leading-relaxed">
              ScamCheck is a free, educational tool designed to help users identify potential traffic ticket and toll notice scams. It provides:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-body text-body leading-relaxed mt-3 space-y-1">
              <li>A Scam Logic Quiz for self-assessment</li>
              <li>A directory of official government (.gov) websites</li>
              <li>Information about toll fraud alerts</li>
              <li>Resources for reporting scams</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-heading-md font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Not Legal Advice</h2>
            <p class="text-body text-body leading-relaxed">
              The information provided on ScamCheck is for general educational and informational purposes only. It does not constitute legal, financial, or professional advice. Always consult with qualified professionals and verify information with official government sources before taking action.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-heading-md font-semibold text-ink mb-3">No Guarantees</h2>
            <p class="text-body text-body leading-relaxed">
              While we strive to provide accurate and up-to-date information, ScamCheck makes no warranties or guarantees regarding the completeness, accuracy, reliability, or availability of the information on this site. The scam indicators and quiz results are guidance tools, not definitive determinations.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-heading-md font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p class="text-body text-body leading-relaxed">
              In no event shall TrafficTicketScamCheck.com or its operators be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of or related to your use of this website. You use this site at your own risk.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-heading-md font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Third-Party Links</h2>
            <p class="text-body text-body leading-relaxed">
              ScamCheck contains links to third-party websites, including government resources. These links are provided for convenience only. We do not endorse and are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or availability of external sites.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-heading-md font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p class="text-body text-body leading-relaxed">
              All content, design, graphics, and organization of ScamCheck are owned by TrafficTicketScamCheck.com and are protected by copyright and other intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without written permission.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-heading-md font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Modifications</h2>
            <p class="text-body text-body leading-relaxed">
              We reserve the right to modify or discontinue any part of this website at any time without notice. We may also update these terms periodically. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-heading-md font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Contact</h2>
            <p class="text-body text-body leading-relaxed">
              If you have questions about these Terms & Conditions, please visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-link hover:text-link-hover underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors">Contact Us</a> page.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
